    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Action or process of creating illumination, which comprises paintings and other adornments applied to books, scrolls, or other document types for the purpose of illustrating or decorating the text. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
